'''Pyramid'''是用[[Python|Python]]书写的[[开源软件|开源]][[web应用框架|web应用框架]]，它基于了[[Web服务器网关接口|WSGI]]。它是受到[[Zope|Zope]]、[[#Pylons框架|Pylons]]和[[Django|Django]]启发的[[极简主义|极简主义]]的web框架<ref name="_doc">{{cite web|title=repoze.bfg introduction|author=Chris McDonough|url=http://docs.repoze.org/bfg/current/narr/introduction.html|accessdate=2010-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230021947/http://docs.repoze.org/bfg/current/narr/introduction.html|archive-date=2013-12-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

Pyramid最初叫做“repoze.bfg”，它获得关注主要在于[[Zope|Zope]]<ref name="poster">{{cite web |url=http://codesinger.blogspot.com/2010/09/zope-summit-dzug-repozebfg.html |title=Zope Summit, DZUG, repoze.bfg |author=Gary Poster |date=2010-09-17 |access-date=2010-09-21 |archive-date=2011-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813195213/http://codesinger.blogspot.com/2010/09/zope-summit-dzug-repozebfg.html }}</ref>和[[Plone|Plone]]社区，随着[[开放社会基金会|开放社会基金会]]的KARL计划从Plone迁移至BFG<ref name="karl">{{cite video |people=Thomas Moroz, Chris Rossi & Calvin Hendryx-Parker |date=2009-10-28 |title=KARL – large-scale Knowledge Management |url=http://plone.blip.tv/file/3037005/ |publisher=Plone Conference 2009 |location=Budapest, Hungary |access-date=2010-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602004608/http://plone.blip.tv/file/3037005 |archive-date=2010-06-02 }}</ref>。在2010年宣布了Pylons框架将于版本1.5转移到使用BFG作为基础<ref name="pylons">{{cite web|title=Emails explaining the Pylons 2 structure|url=http://sluggo.scrapping.cc/tmp/execution/emails.html|author=Ben Bangert|date=2010-09-18|access-date=2010-09-21|archive-date=2022-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220401074839/http://sluggo.scrapping.cc/tmp/execution/emails.html}}</ref>。作为将BFG包括入Pylons计划的结果，BFG被重命名为Pyramid<ref>{{cite web|title=repoze.bfg is now Pyramid|url=http://www.plope.com/bfg-becomes-pyramid|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101113024153/http://plope.com/bfg-becomes-pyramid|archive-date=2010-11-13|access-date=2011-01-03}}</ref>。

===特征===
Pyramid是极简主义的[[跨平台|跨平台]]web框架。它不预知持久性，可以通过[[SQLAlchemy|SQLAlchemy]]集成于SQL数据库或集成于{{en-link|Zope对象数据库|Zope Object Database}}二者，还有其他[[NoSQL|NoSQL]]数据库比如[[CouchDB|CouchDB]]<ref name="_doc" />。

Pyramid允许开发者使用[[正则表达式|正则表达式]]定义映射到对象的路由。同样跟从框架Zope，Pyramid允许层级对象遍历，这里[[URL|URL]]的每个部份都是包含其他对象的对象，这种方式类似于文件系统中的文件夹<ref name="akkerman">{{cite video |people=Wichert Akkerman |date=2009-10-28 |title=Lessons from other frameworks |url=http://plone.blip.tv/file/3224136/ |publisher=Plone Conference 2009 |location=Budapest, Hungary |accessdate=2010-09-21 |time=25:50 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130418172552/http://plone.blip.tv/file/3224136/ |archive-date=2013-04-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===例子代码===
<syntaxhighlight lang="Python">
from wsgiref.simple_server import make_server
from pyramid.config import Configurator
from pyramid.response import Response

def hello_world(request):
    return Response('Hello World!')

if __name__ == '__main__':
    with Configurator() as config:
        config.add_route('hello', '/')
        config.add_view(hello_world, route_name='hello')
        app = config.make_wsgi_app()
    server = make_server('0.0.0.0', 6543, app)
    server.serve_forever()
</syntaxhighlight>

